nl: hmm around for Brand#05 and people in ASIA kind of in HOUSEHOLD segment how are things looking lately by customer vs supplier region
sql:
SELECT rc.r_name AS cust_region, rs.r_name AS supp_region, p.p_brand, COUNT(*) AS trips, AVG(l.l_discount) AS avg_disc
FROM orders o
JOIN customer c ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey
JOIN nation nc ON nc.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN region rc ON rc.r_regionkey = nc.n_regionkey
JOIN lineitem l ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN supplier s ON s.s_suppkey = l.l_suppkey
JOIN nation ns ON ns.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
JOIN region rs ON rs.r_regionkey = ns.n_regionkey
JOIN part p ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
JOIN partsupp ps ON ps.ps_partkey = l.l_partkey AND ps.ps_suppkey = l.l_suppkey
WHERE l.l_shipdate >= DATE '1992-01-01'
  AND l.l_shipdate < DATE '1994-01-01'
  AND p.p_brand = 'Brand#05'
  AND rc.r_name = 'ASIA'
  AND c.c_mktsegment = 'HOUSEHOLD'
GROUP BY rc.r_name, rs.r_name, p.p_brand
ORDER BY trips DESC
LIMIT 15

JOIN supplier s ON s.s_suppkey = l.l_suppkey
JOIN nation ns ON ns.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
JOIN region rs ON rs.r_regionkey = ns.n_regionkey
JOIN part p ON p.p_partkey = l.l_partkey
JOIN partsupp ps ON ps.ps_partkey = l.l_partkey AND ps.ps_suppkey = l.l_suppkey
WHERE o.o_orderdate >= DATE '1993-01-01'
  AND p.p_brand = 'Brand#40'
  AND rc.r_name = 'AMERICA'
  AND c.c_mktsegment = 'FURNITURE'
GROUP BY rc.r_name, rs.r_name, p.p_brand
ORDER BY trips DESC
LIMIT 20
